
# Brain Tumor Dataset from Kaggle: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/masoudnickparvar/brain-tumor-mri-dataset 

Functional MRI (fMRI): Maps brain activity and identifies areas responsible for specific functions, like movement or speech. 
Diffusion Tensor Imaging (DTI): Reveals the structure and integrity of white matter tracts, aiding in surgical planning. 
Magnetic Resonance Spectroscopy (MRS): Measures biochemical changes in the brain, helping to identify tumor type and monitor its progression. 




